Package: securecontext
Title: Memory, Knowledge Persistence, and Context Management for R LLM Agents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "iflores.siaca@hey.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides memory, knowledge persistence, RAG retrieval, and
    token-aware context window management for R LLM agents. Includes
    document chunking, TF-IDF embeddings, vector search, persistent
    key-value knowledge stores, and priority-based context assembly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ian-flores/securecontext
BugReports: https://github.com/ian-flores/securecontext/issues
